node.title: Recap: Blues vs Highlanders
node.description: The Blues have beaten the Highlanders 32-20 at North Harbour Stadium in a tense Super Rugby Pacific match-up.
node.content:
["The Blues have beaten the Highlanders 32-20 at North Harbour Stadium in a tense Super Rugby Pacific match-up.", "", "
\nPhoto: PhotoSport / Brett Phibbs\n
", "The Blues have held on to claim their second win of Super Rugby Pacific after a messy first half saw the Highlanders head into halftime with the lead at 13-3.", "The Auckland franchise now have back-to-back wins, while the Highlanders have picked up four losses.", "Follow the action as it happened:"]
